          <p>
           <img width="432" height="288" src="images/happenings/zoltenJerry.jpg" />
           <strong>
            Congratulations
           </strong>
           to Dr. Jerry Zolten on his work on "The Rise and Fall of Paramount Records, Volume One (1917-1927)", which won a Grammy this year.  Jerry researched and documented the stories of artists on the record. Mirror photo by J.D.Cavrich.
           <a class="bodylink" target="_blank" href="http://www.altoonamirror.com/page/content.detail/id/604794/Breaking-ground--PSU-professor-collaborated-on-boxed-music-set.html?nav=738">
            Click here for link to the story at the Altoona Mirror.
           </a>
