           <strong>
            Alternative Spring Break Trip 2013 Juniata College Hillel: The Dominican Republic
           </strong>
          </p>
          <p>
           This March, Juniata Hillel hosted a service trip to The Dominican Republic. In coordination with the Jewish Organization,
           <em>
            Repairing the World
           </em>
           , and the Dominican host group,
           <em>
            El Guanin
           </em>
           , approximately 15 Juniata students worked together in a Dominican community called La Piedr.
          </p>
